3. cs.RO - The paper deals with exploration of graph-structured state-spaces, which is a common problem in robotics and falls under the category of robotics and control. 
4. cs.SY - The proposed framework involves a reinforcement learning problem, which is a common approach in control systems and falls under the category of systems and control. 
5. cs.SE - The paper applies the proposed framework to the challenging problems of coverage-guided software-testing of domain-specific programs and real-world mobile applications, which falls under the category of software engineering.
